### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = tu_token_aqui

### ================================================
### SPECIES - Especies
### ================================================

### 1. Obtener todas las especies
GET {{baseUrl}}/species
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Obtener todas las especies (incluyendo inactivas) - Solo Admin
GET {{baseUrl}}/species?includeInactive=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Obtener una especie por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/species/uuid-de-especie
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Obtener razas de una especie
GET {{baseUrl}}/species/uuid-de-especie/breeds
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Crear una nueva especie - Solo Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/species
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Tortuga",
  "description": "Testudines",
  "isActive": true
}

### 6. Actualizar una especie - Solo Admin
PUT {{baseUrl}}/species/uuid-de-especie
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Tortuga",
  "description": "Testudines - Actualizado",
  "isActive": true
}

### 7. Eliminar (desactivar) una especie - Solo Admin
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/species/uuid-de-especie
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ================================================
### BREEDS - Razas
### ================================================

### 1. Obtener todas las razas
GET {{baseUrl}}/breeds
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Obtener todas las razas (incluyendo inactivas) - Solo Admin
GET {{baseUrl}}/breeds?includeInactive=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Obtener una raza por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/breeds/uuid-de-raza
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Crear una nueva raza - Solo Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/breeds
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "speciesId": "uuid-de-especie",
  "name": "Pitbull",
  "description": "American Pit Bull Terrier",
  "isActive": true
}

### 5. Actualizar una raza - Solo Admin
PUT {{baseUrl}}/breeds/uuid-de-raza
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pitbull Americano",
  "description": "American Pit Bull Terrier - Actualizado",
  "isActive": true
}

### 6. Eliminar (desactivar) una raza - Solo Admin
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/breeds/uuid-de-raza
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

